<h1 class="title ">
All Nobel Prizes </h1>
</section>
<section class="page-section">
<section class="page-content border-top">
<article class="  entry entry-gutenberg">
<p class="ingress">Between 1901 and 2023, the Nobel Prizes and the Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel were awarded 621 times to 1000 people and organisations. With some receiving the Nobel Prize more than once, this makes a total of 965 individuals and 27 organisations. Below, you can view the full list of Nobel Prizes and Nobel Prize laureates.</p>
<h5 class="wp-block-heading">Find all prizes in | <a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-nobel-prizes-in-physics/">physics</a> | <a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-nobel-prizes-in-chemistry/">chemistry</a> | <a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-nobel-laureates-in-physiology-or-medicine/">physiology or medicine</a> | <a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-nobel-prizes-in-literature/">literature</a> | <a href="http://nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-nobel-peace-prizes/" target="_blank">peace</a> | <a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-prizes-in-economic-sciences/">economic sciences</a> | <a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/lists/all-nobel-prizes/">all categories</a></h5>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity">
