</h3>
<div class="card-prize--laureates">
<div class="card-prize--laureates --three">
<div class="card-prize--laureates--links">
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/medicine/2020/alter/facts/">
Harvey J. Alter</a>,
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/medicine/2020/houghton/facts/">
Michael Houghton</a> and
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/medicine/2020/rice/facts/">
Charles M. Rice</a> </div>
<blockquote class="card-prize--laureates--motivation --last">
“for the discovery of Hepatitis C virus” </blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card-prize">
<h3>
<a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/literature/2020/summary/">
The Nobel Prize in Literature 2020 </a>
</h3>
<div class="card-prize--laureates">
<div class="card-prize--laureates --one">
<div class="card-prize--laureates--links ">
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/literature/2020/gluck/facts/">
Louise Glück</a>
</div>
<blockquote class="card-prize--laureates--motivation
	--last		">
“for her unmistakable poetic voice that with austere beauty makes individual existence universal” </blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card-prize">
<h3>
<a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/peace/2020/summary/">
The Nobel Peace Prize 2020 </a>
</h3>
<div class="card-prize--laureates">
<div class="card-prize--laureates --one">
<div class="card-prize--laureates--links ">
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/peace/2020/wfp/facts/">
World Food Programme</a>
</div>
<blockquote class="card-prize--laureates--motivation
	--last		">
“for its efforts to combat hunger, for its contribution to bettering conditions for peace in conflict-affected areas and for acting as a driving force in efforts to prevent the use of hunger as a weapon of war and conflict” </blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card-prize">
<h3>
<a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/economic-sciences/2020/summary/">
The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel 2020 </a>
