<div class="card-prize--laureates--links">
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/economic-sciences/2020/milgrom/facts/">
Paul R. Milgrom</a> and
<a class="card-prize--laureates--links--link" href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/economic-sciences/2020/wilson/facts/">
Robert B. Wilson</a> </div>
